(495,'pricing','Harga Weight Management','Berapa harga Weight Management?','Weight Management: Rp 550.000 per sesi (90-120 menit). Cocok untuk manajemen berat badan. Termasuk konsultasi, terapi, dan follow-up guidance.','weight,management,harga,biaya',8,1,'2025-12-25 17:57:25','2025-12-25 17:57:25'),
